This leadership contributed into the betterment of the entire nation. Namibia is among the sub region countries that have maintained peace, governance and democracy within their territories.

The unique thing about Namibia is that it has a stable democratic environment which influences political and legislative activities in the country. There exists constant interaction between the citizens and their leadership. This relationship is characterized by cordiality and trust which is a symbol of a happy nation. From the point of view of political activities Namibia is unique and different in all ramifications.

That is why political transparency is one of the pillars of development. There is no room for unnecessary attachments between people who are politically different since the overarching law is respected by all the politicians. The removal of such democratic improverishment is a clear declaration that Namibia is genuinely headed for prosperity.

It is when there is existence of effective political and democratic role that both business and investment can grow to their desired levels. Namibia as a nation of stability under the visionary leadership of H.E Hifikepunye Pohamba, might even be ready to compete with the rest of the more developed countries in terms of development due to the high level of peace and development.
